description:
PhotoshopXPortable.CS6.Incl.Bridge.Rev.1.0-PortableApps.comFormat

NOTE: only download CameraRaw plugin if you need it.

Website: http://www.adobe.com/products/photoshopextended.html
Version: CS6 Extended
License: $999.00 USD
Language: English
Portable Format: PAF (PortableApps.com)
Stealth: Yes (http://www.portablefreeware.com/faq.php#stealth)
Dependency: Admin Rights
Requirements: XP SP3 and later

How to Extract: extract to desired location, launch &quot;PhotoshopXPortable&quot;.

How to Install CameraRaw Plugins: point to &quot;PhotoshopXPortable, install.
(only install if you need it, due to it's size.. it will increase load-time)

How to Use Bridge: simply launch &quot;PhotoshopXPortable&quot; first.
(can communicate with Photoshop)

Synopsis: this version is for minimalists who prefer portable apps. but would
like to have Photoshop + Bridge..

Note: 
* this is a revision to my previous releases.
* instead of releasing a patch, which causes confusion, i decided to repack
everything.
* do not use if you have PS installed.

Revison 1.0:
* massive performance tweaks
* cleaned up coding
* faster load-time
* added support for Visual C++

----------------------------------------------------------------------
FOR ALL THE WHINERS THAT KEEP COMPLAINING ABOUT 3D NOT BEING AVAILABLE
